{
  "texts": [
    "Humans' ability to give digital help and decision-making in crucial and very complex scenarios is greatly enhanced by industrial processes and equipment supported by AI systems [34].",
    "Therefore, it is in the public sector's best interest to fully exploit AI's potential advantages.",
    "AI should not be seen as introducing new technology because it is already in use and will certainly be used in the future.",
    "According to the first government departments to adopt AI, the economy benefits from the technology's increased productivity [40].",
    "Many public sector organizations could benefit from public officials implementing AI."
  ]
}